{
  "stem": "18813.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a gorgeous woman stay beside him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and I said to my husband, you know, that's Schindler?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, you see, I told you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't cry so much because you imagine already things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Go out.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went to the woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, could you tell me what's the man's name what's sitting there writing?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she said, that's Oskar Schindler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I went to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we made movies-- we're together because my husband had the camera with him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I had the movies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I don't where the camera with the movie because I never packed-- when I moved out from the house, I, I couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So Lyliane took over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she-- but whatever happened, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was with us I've seen him after the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he was so changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was so skinny already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But he was an alcoholic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A good man-- he saved lots of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not only I can say what he saved us, was 1,200.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, one day, they brought-- if you have a minute, I can still talk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Came a transport from someplace from Europe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was wintertime.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everything was frozen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could hear only some voices inside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He opened that transport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And people start to fall out because they were dead, frozen to death.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But there was some life-- were the few who had life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We asked them to go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't want to because they were scared that's Auschwitz, or whatever it is, especially they had to go under the shower, the warm water, to defrost completely.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were scared to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the boys were going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The women were going, just to show them that it's life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can stay here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You, you are free.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
